	Closes #200
	* ext/posix/sys/socket.c (sockaddr): Document all optional fields.
	* NEWS.md: Update.
	Reported by Bernd Eggink

	slingshot: sync with upstream for lua 5.3.0 final support.
	* slingshot: Sync with upstream.
	* .travis.yml: Regenerate.

